    <item>
      <title>股价低迷，阿里巴巴彻底改革激励措施以吸引员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/alibaba-overhauls-incentives-to-entice-staff-as-stock-languishes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿里巴巴集团控股有限公司将于4月起推出新的股权与现金相结合的员工激励计划，这是一项重大调整，旨在帮助这家电子商务巨头在激烈的竞争中吸引和留住人才。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/alibaba-overhauls-incentives-to-entice-staff-as-stock-languishes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 07:42:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Naspers 支持的初创公司获得债务融资以削减欧元债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/naspers-backed-startup-gets-debt-funding-to-cut-euro-obligations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Planet42 表示，它从标准银行集团有限公司筹集了本币债务和股权融资，以帮助这家专注于南非的先租后买初创公司偿还昂贵的欧元计价贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/naspers-backed-startup-gets-debt-funding-to-cut-euro-obligations</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 06:37:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
